<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 08:09:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>兼顾军事义务和财产法：以色列国防军预备役学生努力跟上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/juggling-military-duty-and-property-law-students-in-reserves-struggle-to-keep-up/0000018d-3cdc-d02c-a79f-7fdfbe900000</link><description>随着以色列学年的开始，大学试图帮助从战争中退伍的学生补上他们错过的材料。然而，并不是每个人都能参加，有些参加的人也很难集中注意力。一位讲师表示，“显然他们正在付出代价”</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:01:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/juggling-military-duty-and-property-law-students-in-reserves-struggle-to-keep-up/0000018d-3cdc-d02c-a79f-7fdfbe900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国务卿极右翼警察部长尽管不符合标准但仍获得持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/secretary-of-far-right-israeli-minister-gets-gun-permit-despite-not-meeting-criteria/0000018d-3d30-d02c-a79f-7fbbf7cb0000</link><description>为尼利·卡多什颁发执照的高级军官奥菲尔·布基 (Ofir Buki) 在签署请求几天后就晋升为指挥官</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/secretary-of-far-right-israeli-minister-gets-gun-permit-despite-not-meeting-criteria/0000018d-3d30-d02c-a79f-7fbbf7cb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称没有迹象表明恐怖分子渗透到黎巴嫩边境附近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-live/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3e9c-d02c-a79f-7f9f6f250000</link><description>在黎巴嫩边境附近发现可疑人员的报告后，以色列国防军表示对该地区的扫描没有发现渗透的迹象 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队与杰宁当地武装部队之间发生武装冲突 ■ 以色列国防军正在调查近东救济工程处的袭击，称不是由于以色列国防军空袭或炮火造成的 ■ 国际法院将于周五发布裁决，南非外交部长预计将出席听证会 ■ 以色列消息人士称双方远未就新的人质协议达成一致 ■ 美国军方证实胡塞武装向悬挂美国国旗的船只开火</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 03:21:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-live/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3e9c-d02c-a79f-7f9f6f250000</guid></item><item><title>艾哈迈德·阿布·拉蒂夫喜欢“将不同文化融合在一起”。他在葬礼上又做了一次</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/ahmad-abu-latif-loved-to-bring-cultures-together-he-did-it-again-at-his-funeral/0000018d-3d35-d02c-a79f-7fbf38c10000</link><description>尽管下着雨，而且几乎一片漆黑，数百人——犹太人和阿拉伯人、宗教人士和世俗人士、年轻人和老年人——聚集在一起参加中士的葬礼。一等兵（后）艾哈迈德·阿布·拉蒂夫，自愿参加战斗并于周一在加沙地带被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 01:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/ahmad-abu-latif-loved-to-bring-cultures-together-he-did-it-again-at-his-funeral/0000018d-3d35-d02c-a79f-7fbf38c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军参谋长反击监察机构调查，凸显与内塔尼亚胡的紧张关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-chief-pushes-back-against-watchdog-probe-highlighting-tension-with-netanyahu/0000018d-3d38-d35c-a39f-bf7a03fe0000</link><description>哈莱维表示，国家审计长计划在战争仍在进行时调查以色列国防军的行为，这是史无前例的，这将阻止军队实现其目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 00:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-chief-pushes-back-against-watchdog-probe-highlighting-tension-with-netanyahu/0000018d-3d38-d35c-a39f-bf7a03fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代理监狱管理局局长的第一步：巴勒斯坦恐怖分子面临更严酷的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/acting-prison-service-chiefs-first-steps-harsher-conditions-for-palestinian-terrorists/0000018d-3d1c-d02c-a79f-7f9f17a50000</link><description>新任命的监狱长科比·雅科比 (Kobi Ya&amp;#39;akobi) 誓言要对恐怖分子囚犯实行更严厉的监狱条件，但此前曾谈到改善犹太恐怖分子嫌疑人的条件。作为伊塔马尔·本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben Gvir) 的私人朋友，雅科比将“遵守极右翼部长的政策”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/acting-prison-service-chiefs-first-steps-harsher-conditions-for-palestinian-terrorists/0000018d-3d1c-d02c-a79f-7f9f17a50000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔严厉斥责内塔尼亚胡涉嫌将其标记为“有问题”：可能会破坏加沙的调解努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3d27-d35c-a39f-bf7f63970000</link><description>以色列总理批评多哈角色的录音曝光后，卡塔尔外交部发言人指责内塔尼亚胡“出于政治原因”故意阻碍调解努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3d27-d35c-a39f-bf7f63970000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院周五就以色列种族灭绝案中的加沙紧急措施做出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-gaza-emergency-measures-in-israel-genocide-case-on-friday/0000018d-3d12-dc44-a5bf-bdb684e80000</link><description>在即将做出的裁决中，法院不会处理以色列是否在加沙实施国家主导的种族灭绝的主要问题，而只会决定是否发布紧急命令，以防止争端进一步恶化，同时法院继续调查完整案例</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 20:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-gaza-emergency-measures-in-israel-genocide-case-on-friday/0000018d-3d12-dc44-a5bf-bdb684e80000</guid></item><item><title>“你在为哈马斯火上浇油！”：那么，什么时候是为人质而战的最佳时机呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-eradication-of-hamas-will-take-time-the-hostages-dont-have/0000018d-3c53-d02c-a79f-7fdbe1f50000</link><description>当以色列妇女面临以色列人的尖刻批评时，他们称她们的抗议活动是在“助长哈马斯”，要求达成释放加沙俘虏的协议，我们必须问：那么，什么时候为释放人质而奋斗是合适的呢？</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 18:54:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-eradication-of-hamas-will-take-time-the-hostages-dont-have/0000018d-3c53-d02c-a79f-7fdbe1f50000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装对以色列和西方的袭击使也门名声大噪——但也门人的情况又如何呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthi-attacks-on-israel-put-yemen-on-the-map-but-what-is-it-like-for-yemenis/0000018d-367e-d58f-a3af-b77efd440000</link><description>也门长达十年的内战对这个拥有 3300 万人口的本已贫困的国家造成了毁灭性影响，胡塞运动造成长期水和食物短缺、疫苗武器化和虐待儿童</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 17:27:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthi-attacks-on-israel-put-yemen-on-the-map-but-what-is-it-like-for-yemenis/0000018d-367e-d58f-a3af-b77efd440000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列国防军女性观察员新兵在分配后拒绝在部队服役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/dozens-of-female-idf-spotter-recruits-refuse-to-serve-in-unit-after-assignment/0000018d-3c26-d07d-a79d-fde7dbf60000</link><description>大约 50 名女性新兵被选为观察员，该部队在 10 月 7 日遭到袭击，其士兵在加沙仍被扣为人质，她们显然拒绝接受该部队的任务</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 17:08:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/dozens-of-female-idf-spotter-recruits-refuse-to-serve-in-unit-after-assignment/0000018d-3c26-d07d-a79d-fde7dbf60000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯火箭弹杀死 21 名以色列士兵：加沙制造的串联弹头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rpg-that-killed-21-israeli-soldiers-was-homemade-by-hamas/0000018d-3bca-d35c-a39f-bbda880e0000</link><description>导致建筑物倒塌的RPG发射器70年前首次开发，是一种轻型便携式反坦克武器</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 16:45:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rpg-that-killed-21-israeli-soldiers-was-homemade-by-hamas/0000018d-3bca-d35c-a39f-bbda880e0000</guid></item><item><title>女子因涉嫌袭击以色列部长而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rehovot-resident-arrested-on-suspicion-of-attacking-lawmaker/0000018d-3bdd-d07d-a79d-fbff7cd60000</link><description>环境保护部长伊迪特西尔曼对一名 52 岁妇女提出投诉，指控她掌掴和威胁</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 16:32:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rehovot-resident-arrested-on-suspicion-of-attacking-lawmaker/0000018d-3bdd-d07d-a79d-fbff7cd60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队考虑用反坦克导弹武装约旦河西岸定居点的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-weighs-plan-to-arm-west-bank-settlements-with-anti-tank-missiles/0000018d-3b7e-d32b-adcf-ff7e83330000</link><description>此举是应右翼政客和约旦河西岸定居点居民的要求，旨在武装平民安全小组，以抵御 10 月 7 日发生的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 15:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-weighs-plan-to-arm-west-bank-settlements-with-anti-tank-missiles/0000018d-3b7e-d32b-adcf-ff7e83330000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦偷车贼更喜欢电动车型：“你可以照亮房子几天”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-car-thieves-prefer-electric-models-you-can-light-up-a-house-for-a-few-days/0000018d-3b00-d35c-a39f-bb5a3ac90000</link><description>去年汽车盗窃行业大约翻了一番，引发了 5.65 亿美元的保险索赔。在约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦地区，偷来的电动汽车电池甚至被用作发电机</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 14:18:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-car-thieves-prefer-electric-models-you-can-light-up-a-house-for-a-few-days/0000018d-3b00-d35c-a39f-bb5a3ac90000</guid></item><item><title>在有关人质交易的报道中，以色列消息人士称，与哈马斯存在重大分歧，谈判可能会拖延</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/israeli-sources-differences-with-hamas-on-hostage-deal-significant-talks-may-last-long/0000018d-3b53-d3a5-afdf-7f77277d0000</link><description>报道显示，以色列和哈马斯广泛同意在为期一个月的停火期间进行人质囚犯交换。然而，哈马斯拒绝在没有承诺永久停止的情况下谈论细节，并将人质视为维持加沙平静和保护领导人生命的最重要杠杆。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/israeli-sources-differences-with-hamas-on-hostage-deal-significant-talks-may-last-long/0000018d-3b53-d3a5-afdf-7f77277d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的利库德集团部长和极右翼议员将出席以色列“加沙重新安置”会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/netanyahus-likud-ministers-far-right-mks-to-attend-gaza-resettlment-confab/0000018d-3b1e-d35c-a39f-bb5e38070000</link><description>几名以色列议员将于下周日参加在耶路撒冷举行的“胜利会议”，他们声称占领和重新安置加沙地带前以色列定居点是“唯一能带来安全的事情”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:41:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/netanyahus-likud-ministers-far-right-mks-to-attend-gaza-resettlment-confab/0000018d-3b1e-d35c-a39f-bb5e38070000</guid></item><item><title>现在不要向以色列人询问加沙巴勒斯坦人的伤亡情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/dont-ask-israelis-right-now-about-palestinian-casualties-in-gaza/0000018d-3770-d32b-adcf-f77227570000</link><description>最近对以色列人和巴勒斯坦人的民意调查得出了惨淡、令人痛苦的结果 — — 这就是为什么领导人，而不是他们破碎的人民，需要提供摆脱这场灾难的出路。但内塔尼亚胡提供的不是领导力，而是黑暗、冰冷的空虚</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/dont-ask-israelis-right-now-about-palestinian-casualties-in-gaza/0000018d-3770-d32b-adcf-f77227570000</guid></item><item><title>罕见地点：犹太以色列建筑工人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-rare-site-jewish-israeli-construction-workers/0000018d-3b2f-d3a5-afdf-7f3fef790000</link><description>随着以色列建筑业努力取代巴勒斯坦和外国工人，特拉维夫的一个工地找到了雇用最近退役士兵的解决方案</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:14:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-rare-site-jewish-israeli-construction-workers/0000018d-3b2f-d3a5-afdf-7f3fef790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令耶路撒冷在安息日保持公共泳池开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-orders-jerusalem-to-keep-public-pool-open-on-shabbat/0000018d-3b1e-d3a5-afdf-7f3f07570000</link><description>该裁决命令当地社区管理部门遵守耶路撒冷的现状，即宗教与世俗混合社区的公共泳池每周运营 7 天。一位副市长表示，耶路撒冷自由派屈服于宗教胁迫的日子已经结束了</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-orders-jerusalem-to-keep-public-pool-open-on-shabbat/0000018d-3b1e-d3a5-afdf-7f3f07570000</guid></item></channel></rss>